{"about_the_game":"Landoria is a cartoon fantasy strategy game where you begin your campaign in a procedurally generated world as one of the faction leaders to capture strategic locations and defend against the opponents' siege together with your heroes to expand your territory.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Pick your battles wisely</h2>Manage your faction and strategize your expansion in the world map. Control locations that helps you gain access to resources and defend you position. Deploy your armies from your castles to siege enemy castles or intercept their armies. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785890/extras/Store-Description_Deploy.gif?t=1734523413\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Choose your heroes</h2>Discover the strengths and weaknesses of your heroes and pick the best person for your battles. As you win more battles, capture and enlist new heroes into your faction to unite the world.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785890/extras/Store-Description_Lobby.gif?t=1734523413\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The perfect counter.</h2>Use the perfect counter against your opponents by employing different troops, formation and tactics to increase your winning chance. Unleash hero abilities at the correct timing to support your battles.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785890/extras/Store-Description_Formation.gif?t=1734523413\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785890/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734523413","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785890/page.bg.jpg?t=1734523413","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2785890/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734523413","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/app